node.text:
🍼 Oh baby, it's FINALLY HERE! 👼🏽 In between all the late night snacking & cold showers, I've been working SUPER hard behind the scenes to bring you my FIT MAMA-TO-BE pregnancy program! This 12 week plan will show all my expecting mamas how to stay healthy and active, no matter the trimester you are in!

I KNOW just how daunting exercising & eating right can be during this time. Sometimes the last thing you want to do is get up from the couch to move your body (I say that as I'm writing this from the couch 🤣). But to all my mamas out there - I've got you.

Alongside my team of exercise professionals, I've put together all the modified workouts that I've personally been doing the last couple of months - from the lounge room floor to the gym! 💪🏽 It's super freaking important for us to stay active, not only for your physical and mental wellbeing, but also for your little one on board!

Track your mood, energy levels, the foods you're eating - all in one place via the @WBKfit app! It's the virtual pregnancy diary that I've been using every single day. With access to 500+ recipes, pregnancy-safe workouts, tips & tricks, you'll be on your way to become a HOT AF MAMA! Swipe ⏩ for more info!

Make self care a priority. Do this for you & your lil babes!

💗 LINK IN BIO to join 💙

node.text: lookin and feelin like a blueberry with legs lol 🫐🦵🏽🙃 let’s talk pregnancy cravings! especially in the first trimester for me, eating was difficult due to morning sickness (luckily didn’t have it tooooo terribly) but there was a solid few weeks I could not smell food let alone eat much. I lived off of açaí bowls & smoothies. anything frozen or cold I was alll for. I craaaave cold things! I made tons of @blessedprotein smoothies and still do 🙌🏽 blessed is safe for pregnant mamas but of course consult with your doctor first. a regular protein shake just doesn’t do it for me right now 🙅🏽‍♀️ so I like to turn them into smoothies. My current fav flavor is blueberry pie! I make it with a frozen banana, graham crackers, frozen blueberries, dairy free yogurt, oat milk, & lots of ice 🙌🏽 go to www.ehplabs.com & use code katya10 to save $ off your order!
